NG0410:841: nam mkha' thams cad spyod pa gang */

NG0410:1012: gang zag gang la sbyin pa dang *//

NG0410:1014: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0410:1015: slob ma gang la sbyin pa dang *//

NG0410:1023: gzhan gzhung mi dga' smra ba po //

NG0410:1026: srog gi 'byung ba nam mkha' che //
